      "text": "一朵雨做的云",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 50.92,
      "time_str": "00:50.920",
      "text": "云在风里伤透了心",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 55.16,
      "time_str": "00:55.160",
      "text": "不知又将吹向哪儿去",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 59.79,
      "time_str": "00:59.790",
      "text": "吹啊吹吹落花满地",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 64.72,
      "time_str": "01:04.720",
      "text": "找不到一丝丝怜惜",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 69.46,
      "time_str": "01:09.460",
      "text": "飘呀飘飘过千万里",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
      "time": 74.16,
      "time_str": "01:14.160",
      "text": "苦苦守候你的归期",
      "translation": null
    },
    {
